{"tid":2494554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八達通：有人失蹤？我放假wor，星期一先幫你check","createTime":"2021-04-18T15:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T16:38:27.000Z","uid":78892,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f2c582a6b6b3226cec3114abe157e81646b428","tid":2494554,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"八達通公司周六無人上班 無法查使用紀錄<br />\n<br />\nSophie說：「我爸爸成晚無瞓，今朝同媽媽7點幾自己上咗獅子山搵，但乜都搵唔到。」她指出，很想盡力尋找胞妹，「如果搵唔到，我爸爸會後悔一世」。她表示，昨晚（16日）報警後，警方西九龍失蹤人口組今早聯絡她，警員表示已聯絡八達通公司，希望追蹤石樂蕎的八達通使用紀錄，惟八達通公司周六無人上班。Sophie又引述警方稱現時無證據顯示石樂蕎前往獅子山，無法派員搜山。"},{"pid":"8b8f493aecc9cfe574df8190cf2f0a8c139e613c","tid":2494554,"uid":37869,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:59:14.000Z","msg":"批搜查令仲方便過7－11<br />\n救人就等下先"},{"pid":"9ea2d34eb67411e6bb8fb129a8bad27df534c007","tid":2494554,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"咁無計"},{"pid":"4f084c99e31ac366db55912f1c75c3ba1db6c2f7","tid":2494554,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"汁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20210417/s00001/1618650132973/市民尋獲失蹤女子石樂蕎帽子-消防深夜登飛鵝山搜救\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210417%2Fs00001%2F1618650132973%2F%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%8B%E7%8D%B2%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E7%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E8%95%8E%E5%B8%BD%E5%AD%90-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E7%99%BB%E9%A3%9B%E9%B5%9D%E5%B1%B1%E6%90%9C%E6%95%91&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpoLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=1e0a1fb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20210417%2Fs00001%2F1618650132973%2F%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%8B%E7%8D%B2%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E7%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E8%95%8E%E5%B8%BD%E5%AD%90-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E7%99%BB%E9%A3%9B%E9%B5%9D%E5%B